Alvis-Convert version 0.4
================================

This is a module collecting Alvis XML format conversion methods for any 
number of source formats.

Contains these conversion scripts:

    alvis_wikipedia_add_cats
    news_xml2alvis
    wikipedia2alvis
    html2alvis
    html2plain
    ainodump2alvis
    alvisDecollect
    alvisXMLmerge
    alvisXMLsplit
    alvisXMLjoin
    alvisXSL
    alvisSource

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Data::Dumper
   Storable
   Encode
   Encode::Guess
   XML::LibXML
   Compress::Zlib
   HTML::Encoding
   File::Type
   File::Find
   Parse::MediaWikiDump
   Digest::MD5
   MIME::Base64
   Time::Simple
   Carp
   Cwd

Additionally, the scripts in bin/ require:

   File::Copy
   File::Path
   Getopt::Long
   IO::Handle
   Pod::Usage
   POSIX
   Time::HiRes
   Alvis::Pipeline

